<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 14:11:47 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5f7e1fd4772</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这是一座大约建于1220年的古老石头教堂的内部。长椅和讲坛是在宗教改革之后，大约在16至17世纪期间安装的。更多信息请参见#AltText。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="The interior of an old stone church dating from the 13th century. The room is lit only by two large windows in the nave and two smaller ones in the choir – one beside and one behind the altar. All are outside the frame. The floor is covered with timber dating from the 15th century. There are wooden pews on both sides, and a wooden crucifix (approximately from the 12th-century) hangs between the nave and the choir. To the side stands a pulpit, from 1579. The altar consists of a 13th-century altar front in the icon style (figures surrounded by gold leaf) and a wooden altarpiece showing the last supper, from 1699. The altar itself is made of stone. Light from the entrance behind the photographer and indirect light from the right-hand side of the altar make the gold on the altar front gleam. A small sailing ship hangs from the ceiling at the front. This was apparently a tradition in Norwegian churches, after the reformation. It is supposed to point towards the altar, but it points to the left (north) instead. The walls are whitewashed. As the church has neither electricity nor running water, the interior has been surprisingly well preserved." height="2778" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a5f7e1fd4772.jpg" width="2168"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 14:11:47 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5ee14f87954</link><description>&lt;p&gt;帕特拉&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Cachorro dorme com almofada " height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sergio/6a5ee14f87954.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sergio.some.pics"&gt;@sergio&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 03:02:43 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Pascal语录依旧深刻</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5ed58faceb6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我很喜欢《动物森友会：口袋露营》里的引用小工具仍然活跃。不管是谁写了帕斯卡的这些语录，都确实在其中玩得很尽兴。其中不少内容其实还挺有见地的！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Screenshot of the quote widget from Animal Crossing Pocket Camp with Pascal’s face in lower left corner and a quote: “They say the early bird gets the worm, but those evening birds seem to be doing just fine, maaan.” " height="590" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jezlyn/6a5ed58faceb6.jpg" width="1187"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jezlyn.some.pics"&gt;@jezlyn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Jul 2026 02:12:34 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5e8d22f0846</link><description>&lt;p&gt;天空中的文字，纽约（2012）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Words in the sky, New York (2012)" height="2232" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/hiddenflair/6a5e8d22f0846.jpg" width="3968"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://hiddenflair.some.pics"&gt;@hiddenflair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 21:03:35 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5e8bcf0cc4c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;海滩日&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A large Magikarp plushie wearing a multicolored lei sits in the sand at a rocky beach on a cloudy day." height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/plaster/6a5e8bcf0cc4c.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://plaster.some.pics"&gt;@plaster&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 20:57:54 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>